OL,3,CRow over empty #50m music venue as
OL,4,Ccouncil requests 15% tax on residents
OL,6,FCivic leaders in Bradford have
OL,7,Fdefended spending #44million on a
OL,8,Fmusic venue which has yet to open
OL,9,Fafter asking permission to hike
OL,10,Fcouncil tax to between 9.99 and 14.99%.
OL,12,FThe cash-strapped council submitted a
OL,13,Frequest to government last week to
OL,14,Fincrease council tax as it seeks to
OL,15,Fsave hundreds of millions of pounds
OL,16,Fover the next five years.
OL,18,FAn extraordinary meeting took place at
OL,19,FBradford City Hall on Wednesday to
OL,20,Fdiscuss the proposal.
