OL,3,CRow over empty #50m music venue as
OL,4,Ccouncil requests 15% tax on residents
OL,6,FConservative group leader Rebecca
OL,7,FPoulsen criticised the move after the
OL,8,FLabour-run council spent tens of
OL,9,Fmillions on Bradford Live - a project
OL,10,Fto turn the old Odeon cinema into an
OL,11,Fentertainment venue.
OL,13,FShe also cited the cost of setting up
OL,14,Fa trust to run the council's
OL,15,Fchildren's services after it was
OL,16,Fstripped of responsibility following
OL,17,Fthe murder of toddler Star Hobson.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
