OL,3,CRow over empty #50m music venue as
OL,4,Ccouncil requests 15% tax on residents
OL,6,FCllr Poulsen said: "We've had failures
OL,7,Fof children's services and the cost of
OL,8,Fsetting up the children's trust,
OL,9,Fbuilding projects coming in way over
OL,10,Fbudget... Bradford Live sitting empty
OL,11,Fand bringing in no income for the
OL,12,Fdistrict."
OL,14,FBradford Live was initially forecast
OL,15,Fto cost between #22m and #25m, but
OL,16,Fcosts spiralled to #50m, with the
OL,17,Fcouncil putting in #44m.
OL,19,FThe venue is currently lying empty
OL,20,Fafter the operator, NEC group, pulled
OL,21,Fout last year.
