OL,3,CRow over empty #50m music venue as
OL,4,Ccouncil requests 15% tax on residents
OL,6,FThere was further criticism of the
OL,7,Fcouncil's spending on the One City
OL,8,FPark office development, which opened
OL,9,Fin in December 2023 at an estimated
OL,10,Fcost to the council of #28million but
OL,11,Fremains under occupied.
OL,13,FConservative councillor Mike Pollard
OL,14,Fsaid the development "might, with
OL,15,Fluck, today have a market value of
OL,16,F#20million".
OL,18,FLabour councillor Alex Ross-Shaw, who
OL,19,Fis on the regeneration and housing
OL,20,Fcommittee, defended the project.
