OL,3,CRow over empty #50m music venue as
OL,4,Ccouncil requests 15% tax on residents
OL,6,FHe said: "That's the first grade A
OL,7,Foffice development in about 20
OL,8,Fyears... Offices tend to grow over
OL,9,Ftime, they don't start fully occupied,
OL,10,Fso getting them half-full now, in
OL,11,Fterms of the life span, is proving to
OL,12,Fbe a good investment for the district."
OL,14,FLeader of Bradford Council, Susan
OL,15,FHinchcliffe added: "We cannot sustain
OL,16,Fourselves as a low income district in
OL,17,Fperpetuity, we have to change that
OL,18,Fcurve."
