OL,3,CRow over empty #50m music venue as
OL,4,Ccouncil requests 15% tax on residents
OL,6,FShe said submitting the proposal for
OL,7,Fthe tax increase was "not an easy
OL,8,Fdecision".
OL,10,FThe council was given #220 million of
OL,11,Fgovernment funds to keep it afloat
OL,12,Flast year.
OL,14,FIt has set out a range of proposed
OL,15,Fcuts to services, venue closures and
OL,16,Fprice rises, as well as an increase in
OL,17,Fcouncil tax.
