OL,3,CRow over empty #50m music venue as
OL,4,Ccouncil requests 15% tax on residents
OL,6,FIt said it had identified #48.6m of
OL,7,Frevenue savings in 2024/25 with a
OL,8,Ffurther #43.6m of savings earmarked
OL,9,Ffor 2025/26.
OL,11,FBut bosses say a further #50m of
OL,12,Fsavings will need to be made each year
OL,13,Funtil 2030.
OL,15,FThey say council tax is #145 below the
OL,16,Fnational average for metropolitan
OL,17,Fdistrict councils and the lowest in
OL,18,FWest Yorkshire.
