OL,6,FA rise to 14.99% council tax would
OL,7,Fmean residents of band A properties -
OL,8,Fwhich make up 40% of homes in the
OL,9,Fdistrict - would pay #170 extra a
OL,10,Fyear. It would reduce the council's
OL,11,Fneed to borrow by #140 million over
OL,12,Fthe next five years.
